fields.body:
Oregon MarineMap is being developed in support of Goal 19 of Oregon's Statewide Planning which requires the state "to conserve marine resources and ecological functions for the purpose of providing long-term ecological, economic, and social value and benefits to future generations." 

Oregon is developing a comprehensive Territorial Sea Plan to guide uses of the nearshore marine habitats, as well as the siting of renewable ocean energy projects.  The drawing, analysis, and collaborative sharing of nearshore habitats and energy sites will become available to users in the coming months...
fields.title: Welcome to Oregon MarineMap
